<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      body, html {
        height: 100%;
      }
      .communication-image.main-communication-image {
      background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)), url("image/communication.jpg");
      height: 60%;
      background-position: center;
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-size: cover;
      position: relative;
      }
      .communication-text {
        text-align: center;
        position: absolute;
        top: 40%;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        color: white;
        margin-top: 35px;
      }
      .communication-text > img {
        max-height: 400px;
        max-width: 400px;
      }
      .home-card {
        border: none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="communication-image main-communication-image">
      <div class="communication-text">
        <h1 class="mt-3 ml-12">당신을 위한 게시판</h1>
        <br/>
        <h4 class="mt-4 ml-12">게시판을 이용하여 다양한 사람과 소통하세요</h4>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="text-center" style="height: 50%;">
      <h1 class="font-bold mt-5 mb-2">Board</h1>
      <h6 class="font-bold">아래 서비스를 이용해 보세요.</h6>
      <div class="row mx-5" style="margin-top: 80px;">
        <div class="card home-card col-md-4" style="width: 18rem;">
          <div class="card-body">
            <%= fa_icon "users", style: "font-size:60px;" %>
            <h4 class="card-title mt-3">게시글 작성</h4>
            <h5 class="card-subtitle mt-2 text-muted">여러 사람들과 이야기를 공유</h5>
          </div>
          <%= link_to "바로 작성하러 가기", new_post_path, class: "btn btn-warning" %>
        </div>
        <div class="card home-card col-md-4" style="width: 18rem;">
          <div class="card-body">
            <%= fa_icon "thumbs-up", style: "font-size:60px;" %>
            <h4 class="card-title mt-3">좋아요 기능</h4>
            <h5 class="card-subtitle mt-2 text-muted">마음에 드는 게시글을 저장</h5>
          </div>
          <%= link_to "내가 좋아요한 글 보러가기", posts_path(type: :likes), class: "btn btn-warning" %>
        </div>
        <div class="card home-card col-md-4" style="width: 18rem;">
          <div class="card-body">
            <%= fa_icon "comments", style: "font-size:60px;" %>
            <h4 class="card-title mt-3">댓글 기능</h4>
            <h5 class="card-subtitle mt-2 text-muted">게시글에 내 의견을 표현</h5>
          </div>
          <%= link_to "내가 댓글 단 글 보러가기", my_comments_posts_path, class: "btn btn-warning" %>
        </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>